    "USEnglish": "A colorless, odorless <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span> with a relatively short half-life. <br><br>Found in both <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Radioactive</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Frozen</span> atmospheres, this gas is produced by the decay of other high-energy elements."
